在严格模式中：会调用store._vm.$watch(...)，监听state的改动，如果!_committing则会抛出错误。
只能使用mutation更改state
_withCommit (fn) {
  const committing = this._committing
  this._committing = true
  fn()
  this._committing = committing
}
